quran[45]{c,v,t}:
  53,26,Era ba Malayika bameka abali mu ggulu omusanvu nga okuwolereza kwabwe tekugenda kugasa kintu kyonna okugyako oluvanyuma lwa Katonda okukkiriza gwaliba ayagadde era nasiima
  53,27,Mazima abo abatakkiriza nkomerero be bayita ba Malayika amannya ag’ekikazi
  53,28,"Era nga tebakirinaako kumanya kwonna, tebagoberera okugyako okuteebereza ate nga ddala okuteebereza tekulina kye kugasa awali amazima"
  53,29,"N’olwekyo va kwoyo ayawukana nokubulirira kwaffe, naatayagala okugyako obulamu bw'ensi"
  53,30,Ekyo kye kikomo kyabwe mu kumanya mazima Mukama omulabirizi wo yaasinga okumanya oyo abula naava ku kkubo lye era yaasinga okumanya oyo alungama
  53,31,Bya Katonda yekka ebyo ebiri mu ggulu omusanvu n'ebyo ebiri mu nsi (era yye ye nannyini mateeka kwe bikolera) olwo nno alisasula abo abayonoona olwebyo bye bakola era nga alisasula obulungi abo abalongoosa
  53,32,"Abo abeesamba ebyonoono ebinene ne byo buwemu okugyako ebitonotono, (anti) mazima Mukama omulabirizi wo mugazi wa kusonyiwa ye yaasinga okumanya ebikwata ku mmwe, okuva lwe yabatandikawo nga abagya mu ttaka ne mu kiseera we mwaberera mu mbuto za ba Maama ba mmwe, n’olwekyo temwetukuza anti yye yaasinga okumanya ani asinga okumutya"
  53,33,Abaffe olabye oyo akyuka (naava ku mazima)
  53,34,Era nawaayo katono bwamala ate nammira ddala
  53,35,"Abaffe (ekimukozesa ekyo) lwakuba nti alina okumanya ebyekusifu, olwo nno naaba nga abiraba"
  53,36,Oba tabuulirwanga ebyo ebiri mu bitabo bya Musa
  53,37,Ne Ibrahim oyo eyatuukiriza (bwe yalaganyisa Katonda)
  53,38,(Ebyo ebigamba nti) tewali mwoyo gulyetikka kibi kya mulala
  53,39,Era nti omunu tagenda kufuna okugyako ekyo kye yakolerera
  53,40,Era nti mazima okukola kwe kya ddaaki kulirabwa
  53,41,Oluvanyuma alikusasulwamu empeera esinga okuba enzijuvu
  53,42,Era nti mazima ewa Mukama omulabirizi wo yeeri enkomerero (ya buli kimu)
  53,43,Era nti mazima yye yaasesa era yaakaabya
  53,44,Era nti mazima yye yatta era yaawa obulamu
  53,45,Era nti mazima yatonda emitindo ebiri omusajja n'omukazi
  53,46,Abagya mu mazzi agazaala bwe gafulumizibwa (negateekebwa mu kifo ekituufu)
  53,47,Era nti mazima kuli ku ye yekka okusibusa okulala (okuzuukiza)
  53,48,Era nti mazima yye ya gaggawaza era naayavuwaza
  53,49,Era nti mazima yye ye Mukama omulabirizi we munyeenye eyitibwa Shiiraa (abakafiiri gye basinzanga)
  53,50,Era nti mazima yye yazikiriza abe kibiina kya A'adi abasooka
  53,51,Na be kibiina kya Thamud era nga teyalekawo (wadde omu)
  53,52,Na bantu ba Nuhu mu kusooka anti mazima bo be baali basinga okweyisa obubi n'okubula
  53,53,Era ye yae yazikiriza abantu ba be kitundu ekyavuunikibwa (Sodoma ne gomora)
  53,54,Olwo nno ne kikibuutikira ekya kibuutikira
  53,55,Kale olwo kiriwa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabiri wo kyobuusabuusa
  53,56,Ono (omubaka Muhammad) mutiisa ali mu luse lwa batiisa abaakulembera
  53,57,Enkomerero esembedde
  53,58,Tewali ayinza kugizzaayo bweriba ezze mpozzi Katonda
  53,59,Abaffe ebigambo bino bye mujereegerera
  53,60,Nemuba nga museka nemutakaaba
  53,61,Nga nammwe muzannya buzannyi
  53,62,Kale muvunname ku lwa Katonda era mumusinze (ekyo kye kisinga ebya mmwe bye mulimu)
  54,1,Enkomerero esembedde n'omwezi ne gubejjukamu
  54,2,Bwe balaba ekya magero bakyawukanamu ne bagamba nti lino ddogo eritakoma
  54,3,"Olwo nno ne balimbisa era ne bagoberera okwagala kwabwe, so nga buli kigambo kirina engeri gye kirina okubaamu (nungi oba mbi)"
  54,4,Ate nga ddala gaabatuukako amawulire ago agaalimu okukanga (okwandibamaze ne batya Katonda)
  54,5,"(Kur’ani eno) ejjudde amagezi etuukira ddala wala omuntu, (ekyekitalo) okutiisa kwokka tekumala (kwetagisaako okulungamya kwa Katonda)"
  54,6,Kale baveeko (olindirire) olunaku omukowooze lwalikowoola (abantu) kugenda eri ekintu ekitayagalwa
  54,7,"Amaaso gaabwe nga gatunudde wansi, baliva mu kabburi nga balinga ensenene ezisasaanye"
  54,8,"Balisaayirira okugenda eri omukowooze nga abakafiiri bwe bagamba nti, luno lunaku luzito"